Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.43,0:39:50.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.97,0:39:52.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? What stench?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.50,0:39:54.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.67,0:39:55.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Sorry, sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.01,0:39:57.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? What stench?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.84,0:40:00.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Garlic odor  \N-Garlic odor?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.93,0:40:02.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.37,0:40:04.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, its you \N -Stinky! Stinky! Stinky!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.11,0:40:06.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you \N -Stinks so much
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.58,0:40:11.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, finally some success
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.26,0:40:15.73,special_Wed_2_0,,0,0,0,,Truth Revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.27,0:40:15.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's also surprisingly difficult to say "have you eaten garlic?"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.73,0:40:19.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no, its too much
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.70,0:40:21.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd have to say it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.73,0:40:26.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I couldn't even listen to what he was saying
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.21,0:40:30.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Elsewhere with Komiya
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.64,0:40:33.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He found Rice
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.80,0:40:34.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sekimachi is just like a middle-aged woman
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.62,0:40:37.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to popularize that line from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.69,0:40:39.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've been doing it for about 5 years or so
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.93,0:40:41.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.81,0:40:45.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Maybe the next time we come back will be two years from now, so I have to try
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.03,0:40:48.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It had to be said
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.26,0:40:51.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What was your toughest job?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.96,0:40:53.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably LIVE STAND
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.70,0:41:01.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yoshimoto's big comedy festival, LIVE STAND
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.57,0:41:00.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Touching their noses
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.17,0:41:04.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Comedy festival
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.53,0:41:04.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.61,0:41:06.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it stink?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.38,0:41:07.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.26,0:41:08.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you stink, Komiya, or is it outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.85,0:41:10.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Is it outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.78,0:41:17.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's hard... "LIVE STAND" in front of thousands of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.29,0:41:20.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks. Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.02,0:41:23.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks so bad I can't even talk
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.29,0:41:24.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.76,0:41:27.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you eat the garlic?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.14,0:41:28.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.12,0:41:33.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So Komiya also managed to pass
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.62,0:41:35.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so fast
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.14,0:41:39.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Komiya's a good choice since he's a junior
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.21,0:41:41.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it depends on the person
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.20,0:41:45.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As expected, both groups commented on their juniors
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.24,0:41:46.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'd say it to my juniors
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.52,0:41:54.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto, a veteran with few seniors to talk to easily, is in a dangerous situation
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.53,0:41:59.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're a senior, it can't be said
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.40,0:42:05.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, we met Kasuga, who wanted to say something, but the result was the same
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.77,0:42:07.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nowadays
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.56,0:42:12.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The other guy didn't even flinch
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.34,0:42:19.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I won't eat garlic, i'll put it in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.88,0:42:24.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After the garlic, Fujimoto's next target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.75,0:42:26.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go\N You scared the shit out of me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.77,0:42:28.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scared me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.22,0:42:29.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He'll say it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.97,0:42:33.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Despite being a junior, we have high hopes for Daisuke Miyagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.40,0:42:36.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He'll surely say something
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.43,0:42:39.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's got to say something
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.30,0:42:41.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello\N-Hello, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.00,0:42:44.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Daisuke, it's been a long time, hasn't it? \N -Long time no see
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.17,0:42:45.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You scared me. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.45,0:42:48.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a TBS year-end special.\N  -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.21,0:42:51.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I interview you? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.21,0:42:55.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, can I tell you something?\N  -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.52,0:42:57.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.05,0:43:00.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of all the jobs you've had this year. \N -Stinks, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.52,0:43:02.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.26,0:43:03.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?  \N -Don't you smell the stench?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.89,0:43:06.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stink? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.33,0:43:11.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \N It stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.14,0:43:14.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.17,0:43:15.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Daisuke you...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.21,0:43:18.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks! What's that smell? It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.24,0:43:20.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks, doesn't it?  \N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.41,0:43:22.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks too much \N -Let me do the interview
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.55,0:43:25.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? I'm pissed off
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.18,0:43:26.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?  \N-It stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.25,0:43:29.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.89,0:43:35.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're definitely bad. You've got stomach problems. You're overworked. Your breath stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.06,0:43:37.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stand up. What do you look like?  \N-I'm serious
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.29,0:43:40.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stop talking for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.36,0:43:42.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why is that? \N -Your mouth stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.23,0:43:44.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What? Can an interviewer be like this you asshole?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.70,0:43:45.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.53,0:43:47.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is, but it just stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.60,0:43:49.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just smelled it and I almost threw up
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.87,0:43:51.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's this? \N -Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.31,0:43:54.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're so rude
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.18,0:43:56.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's not right. It's not right. It's not right
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.35,0:43:58.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.61,0:44:01.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks. Seriously, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.45,0:44:02.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell? \N -Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.52,0:44:06.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tell me what your hardest job has been
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.76,0:44:10.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let me think
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.79,0:44:12.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.63,0:44:13.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Yeah" stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.53,0:44:16.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.70,0:44:19.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what did you eat? Seriously, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.17,0:44:22.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I have one breath please?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.68,0:44:30.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It stinks
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.15,0:44:31.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Garlic and meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.88,0:44:35.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.35,0:44:38.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He said it! \N -What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.99,0:44:43.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So Fujimoto finally passed after the sixth try
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.26,0:44:47.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Daisuke, you're the first to point it out.  \N-No way
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.56,0:44:50.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably because i've been speaking to juniors
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.57,0:44:52.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But if you think about it, you're a junior too
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.70,0:44:54.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I think about it, he's a junior too
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.77,0:44:55.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.64,0:45:00.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H3732FF&}In summary\N{\r}The juniors basically don't point out problems
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.37,0:45:02.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very fun
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.61,0:45:05.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why is it so funny to see people get hit by bad smells?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.64,0:45:06.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.85,0:45:09.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Daisuke's reaction was very funny
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.60,0:45:12.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I met Fujimoto on that day
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.42,0:45:15.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just wandering round the TV station
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.07,0:45:17.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You met him while they were filming?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.30,0:45:19.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He stank \N  -Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.49,0:45:20.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.37,0:45:25.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I met him, I greeted him
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.26,0:45:30.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I said something smelled bad, and he said, "Don't worry, its because of Wednesday Downtown"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.55,0:45:32.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He explained
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.54,0:45:35.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought you wouldn't say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.73,0:45:38.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's a good point
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.66,0:45:42.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even I would say it stinks
